- January 2018: $2,631.49 AOV from 52 orders, highlighting consistent mid-tier spending.

‚úÖ Insight: Certain months had higher spending per order, meaning customers may be buying premium products.
‚úÖ Action: Focus on premium product marketing for months with high AOV.

Final Business Recommendations
üìå Boost Stock & Promotions in Peak Months: April & January show strong demand‚Äîensure inventory matches demand.  
üìå Target Premium Customers:September 2018 and January 2018 had high-value purchases ‚Äîexpand marketing for premium buyers.  
