The inventory turnover rate of 4,722 indicates how frequently Kuzebikes' inventory is sold and replaced within a given period.  

üìå What This Means
‚úÖ High Turnover Rate (4,722) suggests that products are selling quickly, meaning strong demand and efficient stock management.  
‚úÖ Total Sales: $8,578,988.88 confirms significant revenue, reinforcing that the business is moving large volumes of inventory.  
‚úÖ Average Sales per transaction: $1,816.81, meaning customers tend to make purchases around this value per order.  

üìà Business Implications & Strategies
- Optimize inventory restocking to ensure popular products remain in stock.  
- Reduce holding costs by prioritizing fast-moving products.  
- Review slow-moving stock to avoid excess inventory that ties up resources.  
- Negotiate supplier contracts to align with high turnover rates and maintain seamless supply chain operations. 
